  <brief_title>ED50 of Dexmedetomidine to Prevent Emergence Agitation in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>ED50 of Dexmedetomidine for Reduction of Emergence Agitation Incidence Undergoing Tonsillectomy or Adenoidectomy in Desflurane Anesthesia Following Sevoflurane Induction in Children</official_title>
